8:
Yep! Mama said she found me on a
hot day!
9:
It's getting hot lately, so it's almost
my birthday!
12: Not one for details, are you?
14:
In any case, everyone should get
something on their birthday. What
would you like for your birthday?
19:
Another member for the pack! The
more, the merrier!
22: I knew she'd say something like that.
25: Guess our crew's not cutting it, huh?
29:
Mama's pack had way, WAY more
wolves!
30:
I wanna whole bunch of members,
just like Mama did!
33:
Considering how many of us are in
Starview, that's pretty impressive.
35:
Hmm... Where could we find
someone for her?
38:
You don't HAVE to humor her, you
know.
43:
I mean, this sounds like more trouble
than it's worth.
45:
Why don't you just tell her to ask for
something else?
63:
Your new companions are waiting
for you.
75:
You betcha! And startin' today, we're
part of the Kharo pack!
77:
Is this a dream? Where did you all
come from?!
81:
This is no dream, Kharo. As newly
anointed members of your pack, we
ask you to guide us... O, Pack Leader.
84:
We'll follow you to the ends of the
world, every world!
87:
The ends of the world... Okay,
everybody! Just follow my lead!
93: Looks like she tuckered herself out.
101: You guys nailed it! Thanks a bunch.
104: Sorry for asking such a silly favor.
109:
No worries! I love group exercises
like this, yeah? It was no biggie.
112:
Agreed. I'd be glad to help out again
anytime.
116:
Mngh... Follow me... everybody... I'm
the pack... leader...
124:
Rise and shine, Kharo. We made you
a special birthday breakfast!
129:
Alk! Nimbus! Where... where's my
pack?
139:
You must've been dreamin' or
somethin'.
152:
Yeah! It was sooo much fun! Lemme
tell you about it!
161:
You know... I think we might've just
found ourselves a new pack
member.
